HEADWORD: Cowberry
<hw>Cow"ber`ry</hw> <pr>(-b⟦ecr⟧r`r⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Cowberries</plw> <pr>(-r⟦icr⟧z)</pr>.</plu>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of <gen>Vaccinium</gen> (<spn>Vaccinium
Vitis-id⟦ae⟧a</spn>), which bears acid red berries which are sometimes
used in cookery; -- locally called <altname>mountain
cranberry</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

